    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <bold>IADLXSmartAccessMemory</bold> interface enables AMD Ryzen processors to utilize the full potential of the graphics card memory by utilizing the bandwidth of PCI Express to reduce bottlenecks and increase gaming performance, especially in an all-AMD setup.</para>
<para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="no"><para>InterfaceId:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXSmartAccessMemory</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Smart Pointer Interface Name:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXSmartAccessMemoryPtr</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherits:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_interface" kindref="compound">IADLXInterface</ref></para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherited By:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>N/A</para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
