</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_smart_access_memory__is_enabled" kindref="compound">IsEnabled</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Checks if AMD SmartAccess Memory is enabled on a GPU.       </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
