</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Checks if AMD SmartAccess Memory is supported on a GPU.       </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_smart_access_memory__set_enabled" kindref="compound">SetEnabled</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>This method is deprecated. To enable or disable the state of the AMD SmartAccess Memory, enable or disable Re-Size BAR Support into the system BIOS. <linebreak/>
      </para>
